{"tid":1786896,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"難為李家超 - 古德明","createTime":"2019-12-17T13:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T13:47:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b685a981a4d833a04255dec48866dcf5e85489b5","tid":1786896,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:32:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191217/20826266/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F20826266%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0ggLKV3biakQup4fopcqKIo%3D&h=f695ab03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191217%2F20826266%2F&h=e4f605be\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20191217/20826266/</a><br />\n<br />\n難為李家超 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191217/large/1576485413_5e09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191217%2Flarge%2F1576485413_5e09.jpg&h=0c1ac8d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會民主派提議彈劾偽長官鄭月娥，在朝派反對之餘，卻怕更招民憤，不利明年立法會選舉，於是也痛詆偽政府無能，李慧琼更斥偽保安局長李家超「未能查得是次民變的主腦及金主」。利害關頭，他們絕對不惜毒牙互噬。<br />\n<br />\n《笑林廣記》卷十二有個笑話：某甲好說謊，曾對人說：「我家一井，昨被大風吹往隔壁人家去了。」其僕代為圓謊說：「確有其事。我家的井，貼近鄰家籬笆。昨晚大風，把籬笆吹過井這邊來，卻像井吹在鄰家去了。」某甲又說：「有人射下一鷹，頭上頂碗粉湯。」其僕又說：「此事亦有。我主人在天井內吃粉湯，忽有一鷹墜下，鷹頭正跌在碗內，豈不是鷹頭頂着粉湯。」某甲又說：「寒家（舍下）有頂漫天帳，把天地遮得嚴嚴的，一些空隙也沒有。」其僕攢眉說：「主人脫煞（太過），扯這漫天謊，叫我如何遮掩得來？」中共把香港之官逼民反，硬稱為「海外敵對勢力煽動並資助暴亂」，二零一四年民主佔領運動如此，今日的反暴政運動也是如此。當年，偽長官梁振英言之鑿鑿，說「已掌握敵對勢力煽動並資助」的證據，「適當時會公開」，卻終是空口說白話；今日李慧琼要李家超查得子虛烏有的「民變主腦及金主」，李家超怎能不緊攢八字眉，心想：「主人那漫天謊，教我如何圓得來？」<br />\n<br />\n還是美國國務院說得直截：「北京把香港民變諉過美國非政府組織，無非要淆混是非。」李慧琼對這一點無疑十分清楚，何必還要難為李家超。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com"},{"pid":"67af293c425a968283c1a6a5c26ba9880d09c859","tid":1786896,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=f485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a&amp;oe=5EAED219\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3Df485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a%26oe%3D5EAED219&h=70a59658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d07779c7d967b0591fcdb3a84b857242917b56e","tid":1786896,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母強國咁撚勁唔撚見佢攪鳩美國?"}]}